import { createMuiTheme }  from '@material-ui/core/styles'
const theme = createMuiTheme({
    palette: {
        primary: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.87)[500]",
        primary2Color: "#f57c00",
        primary3Color: "#6d4c41",
        accent1Color: "#ffab40",
        accent2Color: "#ffb74d",
        accent3Color: "#ffe0b2",
        textColor: "#ffffff",
        secondaryTextColor: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78)"
    }
})
export default theme
